\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid3293087 Ann:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid5071929\charrsid5071929 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid16731643\charrsid16731643 
Well, if you watch this programme on the BBC television, on International Women\rquote s Day, there are three programmes starting on March 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\super\insrsid16731643\charrsid16731643 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
