\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902 PAUL:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902 
Well, it appeals to women researchers particularly, and, of course, sociology has become very feminised, so that would be one reason.  The potential audie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid2189439 nce has been growing. And it is}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902  very cogently written.  
