\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid3293087 Ann:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902 Mmm.  There\rquote 
s quite a lot of criticism of that chapter, particularly in the feminist methods literature, but I think that\rquote s good.  The whole point about publishing something like that is, in a way, intended to be provocative, as it was.  It }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902 is}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid6309058\charrsid2046902  to make people think about what they\rquote re doing and the assumptions that they make.
